Body:
The most beautiful names belong to Allah: so call on Him by them;
			but shun such men as use profanity in His names: for what they do
			they will soon be requited. <span class='fn'>1154</span>

To such as Allah rejects from His guidance there can be no guide;
			He will leave them in their trespasses wandering in distraction.
			<span class='fn'>1158</span>
